head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths TIMMONS, MONICA K.

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths TIMMONS, MONICA K.

block.p: TIMMONS-Monica K. On June 19, 2000 of Brooklyn, NY. Beloved daughter of the late Edward & Kathryne McPartland Timmons. Loving sister of Claudia H. Timmons. Dear aunt of David & Marcie. Also survived by many loving relatives. Reposing Fox Funeral Home, Forest Hills, Thursday 7-9 and Friday 2-5 & 7-9 PM. Funeral Mass at Our Lady Queen of Martyrs, Saturday June 24 at 9:15 AM. Interment Calvary Cemetery.
